        "The dataset was stored in Google Drive to ensure it persisted across Colab sessions. All three libraries were installed at the start of the notebook.\n",
        "\n",
        "### 3.2 Baseline Loading (Pandas — No Optimisation)\n",
        "\n",
        "To establish a performance baseline, the full dataset was loaded using default Pandas settings with no optimisation applied. This baseline measurement is the reference point for all subsequent strategy comparisons.\n",
        "\n",
